# ppm.tn: demonstrates the creation of a small (3x2) image
# via a helper method.

# Emits a sequence of red, green, and blue bytes representing a pixel.
def rgb(red, green, blue)
  u8 red
  u8 green
  u8 blue
end

str "P6 3 2 255\n"

rgb 255, 0, 0
rgb 0, 255, 0
rgb 0, 0, 255

rgb 255, 255, 0
rgb 0, 0, 0
rgb 255, 255, 255
